TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT 1 AS BATCH_ID, CG.TRANSACTION_DIST_ID, CG.APPLICATION_NAME, CG.APPLICATION_ID, CG.LEDGER_ID, CG.ORG_ID, CG.EVENT_ID, CG.EVENT_TYPE, CG.EVENT_STATUS, CG.AE_HEADER_ID, CG.AE_LINE_NUM, CG.TRANSACTION_ID, CG.TRX_NUMBER, CG.TRX_LINE_ID, CG.PARTY_ID, CG.PARTY_SITE_ID, CG.PERIOD_YEAR, CG.PERIOD_NUM, COALESCE(CG.AMOUNT,0) AMOUNT, CG.GL_DATE, CG.EXCHANGE_RATE, CG.EXCHANGE_DATE, CG.CURRENCY_CODE, CG.CONVERSION_TYPE, CG.ACCOUNT_CLASS, CG.HEADER_ID, CG.ORDER_NUMBER, CG.ORDER_LINE_ID, CG.QUANTITY_INVOICED, CG.DIST_TYPE, CG.ELEMENT_TYPE, CG.SEQUENCE_NUMBER, CG.CCID, CG.SEGMENT1, CG.SEGMENT2, CG.SEGMENT3, CG.SEGMENT4, CG.SEGMENT5, CG.SEGMENT6, CG.SEGMENT7, CG.SEGMENT8, CG.SEGMENT9, CG.SEGMENT10, CG.DIST_BAL_TYPE, CG.SOURCE_TABLE_NAME, CG.JE_CATEGORY_NAME, CG.JE_SOURCE_NAME, CG.GL_POSTED_DATE, CG.SOURCE_BATCH_NAME, CG.SOURCE_BATCH_ID, CG.DESTINATION_BATCH_NAME, CG.DESTINATION_BATCH_ID, CG.ERROR_MESSAGE, CG.ERROR_FLAG, CG.ERROR_CODE, CG.CREATION_DATE, CG.CREATED_BY, CG.LAST_UPDATE_DATE, CG.LAST_UPDATED_BY, CG.LAST_UPDATE_LOGIN, CG.REQUEST_ID, CG.PROG_APPL_ID, CG.PROG_ID, CG.PROGRAM_UPDATE_DATE, CG.ATTRIBUTE1, CG.ATTRIBUTE2, CG.ATTRIBUTE3, CG.ATTRIBUTE4, CG.ATTRIBUTE5, CG.ATTRIBUTE6, CG.ATTRIBUTE7, CG.ATTRIBUTE8, CG.ATTRIBUTE9, CG.ATTRIBUTE10, CG.ATTRIBUTE11, CG.ATTRIBUTE12, CG.ATTRIBUTE13, CG.ATTRIBUTE14, CG.ATTRIBUTE15, COALESCE(CG.ACCOUNTED_AMOUNT,0) AS ACCOUNTED_AMOUNT, CG.PARENT_SUB_SKU_ID, CG.ATTRIBUTE16, CG.ATTRIBUTE17, CG.ATTRIBUTE18, CG.ATTRIBUTE19, CG.ATTRIBUTE20, CG.ATTRIBUTE21, CG.ATTRIBUTE22, CG.ATTRIBUTE23, CG.ATTRIBUTE24, CG.ATTRIBUTE25, CG.ATTRIBUTE26, CG.ATTRIBUTE27, CG.ATTRIBUTE28, CG.ATTRIBUTE29, CG.ATTRIBUTE30, CG.DATE_ATTRIBUTE31, CG.DATE_ATTRIBUTE32, CG.DATE_ATTRIBUTE33, CG.DATE_ATTRIBUTE34, CG.DATE_ATTRIBUTE35, CG.NUM_ATTRIBUTE36, CG.NUM_ATTRIBUTE37, CG.NUM_ATTRIBUTE38, CG.NUM_ATTRIBUTE39, CG.NUM_ATTRIBUTE40, CG.NUM_ATTRIBUTE41, CG.NUM_ATTRIBUTE42, CG.NUM_ATTRIBUTE43, CG.NUM_ATTRIBUTE44, CG.NUM_ATTRIBUTE45, CG.TRAIL_FILE_NAME, CG.SOURCE_DML_TYPE, CG.SOURCE_COMMIT_TIME, CG.REFRESH_DATETIME, CG.PROCESSED_FLAG, 'CG' AS GLOBAL_NAME, 'I' AS ACTION_CODE, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS CREATE_DATETIME FROM ( SELECT CG.* FROM $$NRTACCUMVWDB.CG1_XXCFIR_REVENUE_DIST_ALL CG INNER JOIN $$ETLVWDB.EL_FND_APPLICATION_AR EFAR ON CG.APPLICATION_ID=EFAR.APPLICATION_ID WHERE UPPER(EFAR.APPLICATION_NAME) IN ('REVENUE ATTRIBUTION') AND EFAR.LANG = 'US' AND SOURCE_COMMIT_TIME >='$$LastExtractDate' QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER () OVER (PARTITION BY TRANSACTION_DIST_ID ,CG.APPLICATION_ID ORDER BY REFRESH_DATETIME DESC)=1 ) CG
WHERE CG.SOURCE_DML_TYPE <> 'DELETE' AND CG.EVENT_STATUS='P'
